assets.description:
tiltbrush sketch I made with oculus.
It is inspired to a bay near lagadakia beach, in Cefalonia. Rocks were standing around this wonderful clean water, and you could see many little creatures swimming around.
No one was there. I tried to imitate the peacefulness of that place with tiltbrush vr , hope it communicates a bit of that summer atmosphere to you guys :)
If you want to follow me on instagram my account is https://www.instagram.com/emiliacomix/
